<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='718527' id='t-718527'>or baffling and puzzling,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='720060' id='t-720060'>are not the results of individuals</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722146' id='t-722146'>acting through their own accord</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='723999' id='t-723999'>but because they are being bent</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='725808' id='t-725808'>to the control of something else.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='728478' id='t-728478'>And while that idea may be disquieting,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='730518' id='t-730518'>and while parasites' habits may be very grisly,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='733441' id='t-733441'>I think that ability to surprise us</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='735233' id='t-735233'>makes them as wonderful and as charismatic</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='738408' id='t-738408'>as any panda or butterfly or dolphin.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:32
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='741772' id='t-741772'>At the end of &quot;On the Origin of Species,&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='743991' id='t-743991'>Charles Darwin writes about the grandeur of life,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='746980' id='t-746980'>and of endless forms most beautiful</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='749633' id='t-749633'>and most wonderful,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='751065' id='t-751065'>and I like to think he could easily have been talking</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='753644' id='t-753644'>about a tapeworm that makes shrimp sociable</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='756824' id='t-756824'>or a wasp that takes cockroaches for walks.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='760073' id='t-760073'>But perhaps, that's just a parasite talking.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='763222' id='t-763222'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='764953' id='t-764953'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
